snippet.title: The Backrooms: Realism - Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Trailer music belongs to Horror Music World! Track's called You Didn't See Anything.
I made this quickly mainly for the GameJolt page, since it didn't have a proper trailer yet. I'll prolly remake it with voice acting and my own music sometime later down the road, but until then, enjoy this and the game, and maybe stay tuned for new updates :P
